00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:19.320
NICK BUTCHER: It's worth
recapping here, as well, the

00:07:19.320 --> 00:07:21.760
rules we tend to think about for
when things should be in

00:07:21.760 --> 00:07:24.800
action, which is immediately
available on the action bar,

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.000
or when things should
get demoted.

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:28.160
Take something like my
profile is going

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:29.250
to be uncommon action.

00:07:29.250 --> 00:07:32.290
You're not going to be clicking
into that many times.

00:07:32.290 --> 00:07:36.160
So that probably should always
go into the action overflow,

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:38.040
similar to how help and settings
and about would

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:41.620
always go in the action overflow
as uncommon actions.

00:07:41.620 --> 00:07:44.715
You wouldn't want to promote
this to an action item, even

00:07:44.715 --> 00:07:47.900
if there was space on a larger
device, because it's not a

00:07:47.900 --> 00:07:48.530
common action.

00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:51.570
ROMAN NURIK: Another thing I
wanted to mention is that if

00:07:51.570 --> 00:07:55.060
you want to encourage the user
to log in to create an account

00:07:55.060 --> 00:07:58.400
for your app, using the overflow
for that is probably

00:07:58.400 --> 00:07:58.840
not a good idea.

00:07:58.840 --> 00:08:00.900
You're probably not going to get
too much engagement there.

00:08:00.900 --> 00:08:02.590
But what you could
do is have like a

00:08:02.590 --> 00:08:03.840
butter bar, or something.

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:07.330
Like a dismissible butter bar
show up along the bottom of

00:08:07.330 --> 00:08:10.320
the screen that says, hey, if
you log in, you get this and

00:08:10.320 --> 00:08:11.710
this value.

00:08:11.710 --> 00:08:14.340
You just kind immediately
explain the benefits, rather

00:08:14.340 --> 00:08:17.690
than showing an icon always
available on screen.

00:08:17.690 --> 00:08:18.780
Just make it contextual.

00:08:18.780 --> 00:08:21.500
If you wanted the user to login
or register, make sure

00:08:21.500 --> 00:08:24.040
that they see a nice, big
prominent bar that they can

00:08:24.040 --> 00:08:28.730
also dismiss if they don't
really want to login.

00:08:28.730 --> 00:08:30.230
So let's move on to the next.

00:08:30.230 --> 00:08:32.630
Actually, this is the
