00:08:40.340 --> 00:08:42.710
So you'd show maybe three or
four items as kind of a

00:08:42.710 --> 00:08:43.690
summary of the post.

00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:46.000
And then at the bottom,
you'd touch all

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.610
listings to take you there.

00:08:48.610 --> 00:08:50.280
So let's look at the drawer.

00:08:50.280 --> 00:08:53.340
So you have right now, if you
touch that top left search

00:08:53.340 --> 00:08:57.630
icon, you get this, I guess it's
