00:09:03.470 --> 00:09:05.900
So Search is kind part
of this bar.

00:09:05.900 --> 00:09:08.370
And it makes sense in terms
of proximity, right?

00:09:08.370 --> 00:09:11.770
The search bar is right next
to the recent searches.

00:09:11.770 --> 00:09:14.850
However, it's somewhat of an
uncommon place for Search.

00:09:14.850 --> 00:09:17.130
Users really expect search
to be in the action bar

00:09:17.130 --> 00:09:18.360
immediately available.

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:22.050
Not two touches away, but
immediately one touch away.

00:09:22.050 --> 00:09:27.590
And it's not really violating
any strong semantic rules for

00:09:27.590 --> 00:09:28.740
the navigation drawer.

00:09:28.740 --> 00:09:31.350
There aren't any actions here,
except for search.

00:09:31.350 --> 00:09:33.380
But it is kind of pushing
the content over,

00:09:33.380 --> 00:09:35.690
pushing the top bar over.

00:09:35.690 --> 00:09:38.555
And so, in terms of the
interaction itself, it's not

00:09:38.555 --> 00:09:39.860
really violating the guidelines,
but it's not

00:09:39.860 --> 00:09:42.550
adhering to the guidelines
that we have set out.

00:09:42.550 --> 00:09:45.860
So what we decided to do is see
what this would look like

00:09:45.860 --> 00:09:48.780
with a proper new navigation
drawer.

00:09:48.780 --> 00:09:51.810
So you have Home at the
top, which is kind of

00:09:51.810 --> 00:09:54.090
your stream, per se.

00:09:54.090 --> 00:09:55.930
And then each of the
other things are

00:09:55.930 --> 00:09:56.820
still represented there.

00:09:56.820 --> 00:10:00.170
We also added a couple of things
like section headers to

00:10:00.170 --> 00:10:03.400
make sure that it's clear
what you're looking at.

00:10:03.400 --> 00:10:04.680
And, yeah, you could
do the same things.

00:10:04.680 --> 00:10:06.850
You can dismiss recent
searches.

00:10:06.850 --> 00:10:10.260
You can switch between different
categories and

00:10:10.260 --> 00:10:11.050
things like that.

00:10:11.050 --> 00:10:14.370
But the core point here is
that since the action bar

00:10:14.370 --> 00:10:16.210
doesn't slide out of the way,
Search is still accessible.

00:10:16.210 --> 00:10:18.455
Search is still an action
that's there

00:10:18.455 --> 00:10:20.390
in the action bar.

00:10:20.390 --> 00:10:22.040
Because it's globally
relevant, it's not

00:10:22.040 --> 00:10:24.960
contextually relevant to the
screen that the navigation

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:26.480
drawer is hiding.

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:28.700
So it's totally fine to leave
that action there when the

00:10:28.700 --> 00:10:32.290
navigation drawer is exposed.

