navigation drawer--

00:11:56.750 --> 00:11:59.740
so they're here, right, pizza
or wearing dresses.

00:11:59.740 --> 00:12:05.660
Since they're represented there,
those screens that you

00:12:05.660 --> 00:12:08.090
get taken to when you press
those should appear in the

00:12:08.090 --> 00:12:08.910
navigation drawer.

00:12:08.910 --> 00:12:10.650
Or should have the navigation
drawer affordance.

00:12:10.650 --> 00:12:12.310
And this is in accordance
with the guidelines

00:12:12.310 --> 00:12:13.350
that we have set out.

00:12:13.350 --> 00:12:15.160
So if you touch something in the
navigation drawer and you

00:12:15.160 --> 00:12:18.340
get taken to a new screen, that
screen should have access

00:12:18.340 --> 00:12:19.870
to the same navigation drawer.

00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:20.970
So you could probably
go either way.

00:12:20.970 --> 00:12:24.610
And a lot of folks think that
on search screens you should

00:12:24.610 --> 00:12:25.420
