00:12:35.990 --> 00:12:37.520
touch it up there.

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:40.090
And then everything else
on this screen.

00:12:40.090 --> 00:12:42.920
Nick, before we move
on, any comments?

00:12:42.920 --> 00:12:45.900
