on Google Play.

00:23:23.120 --> 00:23:25.410
It's a lovely app.

00:23:25.410 --> 00:23:27.470
So here they're doing
something quite

00:23:27.470 --> 00:23:28.300
custom, in a way.

00:23:28.300 --> 00:23:32.190
They're trying to give as much
real estate and space to

00:23:32.190 --> 00:23:35.740
imagery and description, in a
very, very beautiful way.

00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:37.960
So they're bringing very much
their own personality and

00:23:37.960 --> 00:23:40.370
their own information
architecture here.

00:23:40.370 --> 00:23:43.180
But they're kind of blending
that with the Android design.

00:23:43.180 --> 00:23:45.480
So when it comes to things like
navigation and performing

00:23:45.480 --> 00:23:49.850
important actions, here they get
