00:25:25.825 --> 00:25:28.790
the minimum, making content
speak, it's not going to give

00:25:28.790 --> 00:25:32.490
you any kind of advice about
what colors or what palette

00:25:32.490 --> 00:25:34.550
you use in your application.

00:25:34.550 --> 00:25:36.770
This is where you have the
opportunity to bring your own

00:25:36.770 --> 00:25:40.440
personality to an Android app
