00:25:53.530 --> 00:25:55.580
Here they're doing that trick,
using that single, strong

00:25:55.580 --> 00:25:56.270
accent color.

00:25:56.270 --> 00:26:01.370
There's really recognizable
minty green color.

00:26:01.370 --> 00:26:04.500
While this is a pretty stock
action bar, it's instantly

00:26:04.500 --> 00:26:05.970
recognizable, instantly
branded.

00:26:05.970 --> 00:26:09.250
They've done a really nice job
of marrying Android visual

00:26:09.250 --> 00:26:10.975
design with their own
branding, their

00:26:10.975 --> 00:26:12.225
own look and feel.

00:26:14.750 --> 00:26:17.860
ROMAN NURIK: I will say that we
