Some of the examples that we
talked about, Flipboard and

00:28:17.080 --> 00:28:20.770
Grand St., Some of the most
obvious interactions on

00:28:20.770 --> 00:28:23.320
Android are swiping
and scrolling.

00:28:23.320 --> 00:28:25.740
And I'd say that both of those
apps, Flipboard does a little

00:28:25.740 --> 00:28:28.380
bit more custom, but Grand
St. especially.

00:28:28.380 --> 00:28:31.730
It looks very, very custom, but
as soon as you open up the

00:28:31.730 --> 00:28:33.670
