around, and things

00:28:33.670 --> 00:28:35.300
just work as expected.

00:28:35.300 --> 00:28:38.860
So rather than doing really
custom gestural stuff to do

00:28:38.860 --> 00:28:43.480
basic things like navigate
through content, just rely on

00:28:43.480 --> 00:28:46.740
existing features, existing
gestures, like scrolling,

00:28:46.740 --> 00:28:48.840
swiping horizontally,
things like that.

00:28:48.840 --> 00:28:50.173
And users will almost
instantly know

00:28:50.173 --> 00:28:50.940
