00:28:53.250 --> 00:28:57.380
Things like the action bar,
upaffordance, spinners, tabs,

00:28:57.380 --> 00:28:59.620
things like that.

00:28:59.620 --> 00:29:01.320
NICK BUTCHER: Absolutely.

00:29:01.320 --> 00:29:03.860
So it's not like an all or
nothing discussion, right?

00:29:03.860 --> 00:29:06.620
You can't say, I have to be
consistent with my application

00:29:06.620 --> 00:29:08.460
because I'm already on other
platforms and people won't

00:29:08.460 --> 00:29:10.030
