00:29:10.030 --> 00:29:12.310
There absolutely are elements
that you should be consistent

00:29:12.310 --> 00:29:14.650
to, but there's some elements
which it's really important to

00:29:14.650 --> 00:29:16.410
get closer to the Android
patterns.

